The GLib/GTK+ Development Platform

The beginning of a book about development with the GLib/GTK+ platform.

License: Creative Commons BY SA (see the text for more details).

To compile the document:
$ cd src/
$ latexmk -pdf main.tex

A PDF is available at:
https://people.gnome.org/~swilmet/download/download-glib-gtk-dev-platform.php
(If you copy the link on another web page, please copy the *.php URL, not the
direct PDF link, because the *.php page has a download counter, and I like to
have statistics.)
